{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategy without the Sweat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fortitude Tower Defense is everything that makes the genre so enjoyable; real-time action with wave-based decision making. Build and upgrade towers, manage resource production, and train and deploy units to defend your kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3388300/extras/TowerUpgrade.gif?t=1738784931\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you play through three Acts with 10 unique maps, you'll enjoy permanent progression along the way. Improve towers and structures with Requisitions. Buff your forces with Relics (rewards for killing the big baddies). And enhance your Mage Towers through Academy Research.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Feature Spotlight: Territories</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Territory takeover through conquest allows you to claim additional land to build your defenses. Heavy siege weapons recommended!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3388300/extras/TerritoryIsland.gif?t=1738784931\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fortitude takes place in the land of Edaria, a once peaceful continent enlivened by powerful sorcery. It has long since become a warring, fractured island bereft of all magic. Fight to defend your kingdom from domestic troubles, witness the rebirth of the Allstone, and defeat the looming threat that comes from the frosty northlands.\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3388300/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738784931","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3388300/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738784931","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3388300/28acbfc2aa25a861fc7c4be884a72beae877acb9/capsule_23